"{\"uid\": \"cityam.com-murray-tennis-farewell-tour-goes-on-at-paris-2024-olympic-games\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 45, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 47, \"to\": 92, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 94, \"to\": 139, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By:Matt Hardy  Deputy Sports Editor - City AM  Andy Murray's farewell tour oftennislives to fight another day after the Brit and his partner Dan Evans beat Belgians Joran Vliegen and Sander Gille 6-3 7-6 11-9 to reach the quarter-finals of the doubles at the Paris 2024 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 282, \"end\": 291, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Die_Warzau\", \"score\": 0.9596545745311013, \"rank\": 0.0420415900082225, \"text\": \"Dan Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Die_Warzau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Die_Warzau\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The British duo stormed out of the blocks to a 3-0 lead in the first set on the clay courts of Roland Garros before taking the first set 6-3.\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 568, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 431, \"end\": 438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.7244599178978753, \"rank\": 0.35128865907387824, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 522, \"end\": 535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"score\": 0.9999930483527962, \"rank\": 6.860389159635002e-06, \"text\": \"Roland Garros\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Open\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their Belgian opposition offered resistance in the second set with Murray - who has announced that the Paris 2024 Olympic Games will be his lasttournamentas a professional tennis player before retirement - and Evans losing the tie-break.\", \"from\": 570, \"to\": 807, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 576, \"end\": 583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"score\": 0.730887564343999, \"rank\": 0.19298709125090927, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium\"}, {\"begin\": 637, \"end\": 643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9914614550062084e-41, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 780, \"end\": 785, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"score\": 0.9267295620374165, \"rank\": 0.07906266782210834, \"text\": \"Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Godfrey_Evans\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But they went on to win the deciding third set tie-break 11-9 on the clay to progress.\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 895, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They will take on either American third seeds Tommy Paul and Taylor Fritz or Dutch duo Robin Haase and Jean-Julien Rojer.\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 1018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 922, \"end\": 930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999218631661594, \"rank\": 3.356486417420587e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 943, \"end\": 953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Paul\